name: Quantum Physics
about: Physics is the language of the world. Quantum physics is the study of matter and energy at the most fundamental level.

name: Applied Mathematics
about: Mathematics is the mother of Science. Applied mathematics is the application of mathematical methods by different fields such as physics, engineering, medicine, biology, finance, etc.

name: Artificial Intelligence
about: Artificial intelligence (AI) is intelligence demonstrated by machines, as opposed to the natural intelligence displayed by animals and humans.

name: Front-End Web Development
about: Web development is the work involved in developing a website for the Internet or an intranet. Web development can range from developing a simple single static page of plain text to complex web applications.

name: Social Science
about: Social science is, in its broadest sense, the study of society and the manner in which people behave and influence the world around us.
